# Snapshot allow-list for lint-design-tokens.sh.
#
# Regenerated 2026-06-03 against the MackesWorkstation merged tree.
# The inherited MDE allow-list (139 entries) was STALE — it referenced
# an MDE crate layout (mde-applets / mde-panel / mde-workbench / ...)
# and canonical token paths that no longer exist in this monorepo. This
# file is a fresh snapshot of the PRE-EXISTING hardcoded-token drift in
# THIS tree (hex literals + Color::from_rgb outside the canonical sites
# crates/shell/mde-ui/src/palette.rs + data/css/tokens.css), so the gate
# exits 0 today and catches only NET-NEW hardcoded tokens going forward.
#
# Each entry should eventually port to the canonical token sources
# (palette.rs / tokens.css); the file SHRINKS over time. Net-new hits
# outside this list are a regression and fail the gate.
#
# Snapshot count: 317 pre-existing token-drift entries.
#
# Format: one <file>:<line> key per line. Lines starting with `#` are
# comments. Blank lines ignored.

